[Mark 15:34](../../../bib/kjv/mar015.htm#034.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_034">mar 15:34</span></span>

My God, my God, why hast thou forsaken me - Thereby claiming God as his
God; and yet lamenting his Father's withdrawing the tokens of his love,
and treating him as an enemy, while he bare our sins.

